text: DWMN, under the brand name 94.1 Love Radio Tuguegarao, is an FM radio station of the Manila Broadcasting Company operating at Tuguegarao City. Its studio and transmitter is located at 3rd Floor, Sam's Place, Caritan Centro, Tuguegarao City. ==Love Radio stations== :Further information: Love Radio stations ==External links== * Category:Love Radio Network stations Category:Radio stations in Cagayan Category:Adult hits radio stations in the Philippines Category:Radio stations established in 2008
